  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>

        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="AN179.1-kilavi">pirivuṇarttiya talaimaka<supplied>ṟ</supplied>kut tōḻi celavaḻuṅ[ka]c colliyatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">What the confidante said to HIM who informed [her] of the separation, preventing [his] going.</p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="AN179.1">
        <l>viṇṭōy cimaiya viṟalvaraik kavā<supplied>a</supplied>ṉ</l>
        <l>veṇṭē rōṭuṅ kaṭaṅkāy maruṅkiṟ</l>
        <l>viṉaiyeri paranta tuṉṉarum viyaṉkāṭṭuc</l>
        <l>ciṟukaṇ yāṉai neṭuṅkai nīṭṭi</l>
        <l>vāṉvāy tiṟantum vaṇpuṉal pe<supplied>ṟā</supplied>tu</l>
        <l>kāṉpulantu kaḻiyuṅ kaṇṇakaṉ parappiṉ</l>
        <l>viṭuvāyc ceṅkaṇaik koṭuvi lāṭavar</l>
        <l>naṉṉilai poṟitta kaṉṉilai yatara</l>
        <l>virumpukoḷ pūcal kaḷaiyu<supplied>na</supplied>rk kāṇāc</l>
        <l>curañcela virumpiṉi rāyi ṉiṉṉakai</l>
        <l>murunteṉat tiraṇṭa muḷḷeyiṟṟut tuvarvāyk</l>
        <l>kuvaḷai nāṇmalar puraiyu muṇkaṇ</l>
        <l>matiyēr vāṇutal pulampap</l>
        <l>patipeyarn tuṟaita lol<supplied>lu</supplied>mō numak<supplied>kē</supplied>.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>On the slope of the victorious mountain with peaks that touch the sky, (1)</l>
        <l>in the wide wilderness difficult to approach where busy flames spread (3)</l>
        <l>to the side of wild unripe fruit where the mirage runs, (2)</l>
        <l>in the expanse vast in area, where the small-eyed elephant</l>
        <l>extends [its] long trunk [and], without reaching the generous flood,</l>
        <l>although the clouds opened [their] mouths, passes by, vexed with the forest, (4-6)</l>
        <l>if you longed to go to the desert (10a-c)</l>
        <l>where one does not see those who keep away the fight with iron [against iron] (9)</l>
        <l>on ways where are positioned stones that are engraved with the good status (8)</l>
        <l>of men with cruel/curved bows and arrows red at the tip that are discharged,</l>
        <l>would it be possible for you to remain away from home (14)</l>
        <l>so that she will be lonely, [her] forehead bright as the moon, (13)</l>
        <l>with kajal eyes that resemble day[-fresh] waterlily blossoms (12)</l>
        <l>[and] a sweet-smiling coral mouth with thorn teeth that are rounded like sprouts? (10df.)</l>
      </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
  </text>
